data.eml:eml: Two new species of Paramphiascella Lang (Copepoda: Harpacticoida: Miraciidae) from a brackish water pond in Thailand

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Chullasorn, Supawadee (2010): Two new species of Paramphiascella Lang (Copepoda: Harpacticoida: Miraciidae) from a brackish water pond in Thailand. Zootaxa 2634: 1-24, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.198371
